Example code for the Odometry interface.

- PollPosition queries the odometry interface for the current
  position. 

- OdometryStream uses the notfication channel for Odometry event
  delivery.

- SetPosition call's the Odometry interface setPosition method with
  the parameters specified at the command line.

  Usefull to place the robot somewhere in a global coordinate frame,
  while the localization module is not yet perfect...
